    {
      "index": 13,
      "chn": "唷，你好啊。",
      "jap": "やあ、こんにちは",
      "eng": "Aye, siwmae.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "chn": "真没想到这里会有人来啊。",
      "jap": "まさか、人が来るとは思わなかったよ",
      "eng": "I didn't expect to meet anybody here.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "chn": "这表示我们两个喜好都很特殊，嘿嘿。",
      "jap": "お互い物好きってことかな。うん、うん",
      "eng": "I suppose great minds think alike, eh? Heh heh.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "chn": "#0离开传火祭祀场后，返回攀谈",
