    {
      "index": 17,
      "chn": "唷，你好啊。",
      "jap": "やあ、こんにちは",
      "eng": "Aye, siwmae.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "chn": "没想到会在这里遇到你，真是巧遇。",
      "jap": "こんなところで会うなんて、奇遇だな",
      "eng": "Never thought I'd see you here.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "chn": "我有预感会有一笔好交易。",
      "jap": "予感がするよ。いい取引ができそうだ",
      "eng": "This feels karmaic. Pray tell, what do you have for me?",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "chn": "#0未完成交易时，互动列表-选择「交谈」",
      "jap": "#0リストから選択:話す",
      "eng": "#0Menu-Choose \"Talk\" without purchasing something",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "chn": "嗯……",
      "jap": "ふーむ…",
      "eng": "Hmm...",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "chn": "没有什么特别的……",
      "jap": "特に何も無いなあ…",
      "eng": "I'm afraid I don't see anything here.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "chn": "#0第1次完成交易后，互动列表-选择「交谈」",
      "jap": "#0リストから選択:話すA",
      "eng": "#0Menu-Choose \"Talk\" 1st time after purchasing something",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "chn": "嗯……",
      "jap": "ふーむ…",
      "eng": "Hmm...",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "chn": "算了，看在和你应该会有笔不错的交易份上……",
      "jap": "まあ、君とはいい取引ができそうだからね…",
      "eng": "Well, I'm certain we will make a good trade eventually...",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "chn": "我就告诉你吧。",
      "jap": "色々と教えてあげよう",
      "eng": "So, I am willing to share some tips.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "chn": "如果想要地下墓地里的“注火，”就要用神圣武器。",
      "jap": "地下墓地の「注ぎ火」が欲しければ、神聖な武器を使うといい",
      "eng": "If you seek Kindling in the Catacombs, use divine weapons.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "chn": "这应该可以制服苏醒的骸骨。",
      "jap": "よみがえる骸骨をおさえられるだろう",
      "eng": "That will repel the reassembling skeletons.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "chn": "#0第2次完成交易后，互动列表-选择「交谈」",
