      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "chn": "嗯……",
      "jap": "ふーむ…",
      "eng": "Hmm...",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "chn": "算了，看在和你应该会有笔不错的交易份上……",
      "jap": "まあ、君とはいい取引ができそうだからね…",
      "eng": "Well, I'm certain we will make a good trade eventually...",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "chn": "我就告诉你吧。",
      "jap": "色々と教えてあげよう",
      "eng": "So, I am willing to share some tips.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "chn": "小隆德的亡灵受到了诅咒，\r\n一般来说是伤不了他们的，",
      "jap": "小ロンドの亡霊は、呪われているからね\r\n通常じゃあ手も足も出ない",
      "eng": "The cursed Ghosts of\r\nNew Londo are formidable foes.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "chn": "想要伤到他们，就要特殊的武器……或受诅咒的身体。",
      "jap": "何とかしたければ、特別な武器か…呪われた体が必要なのさ",
      "eng": "To face them, you will require special arms...Or a cursed body.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "chn": "如果想早点受诅咒，\r\n一般是要去下水道找眼珠蜥蜴",
      "jap": "手っ取り早く呪われたければ、\r\n下水の目玉トカゲがお勧めだな",
      "eng": "The quickest way to be cursed? \r\nTry the bug-eyed lizards in the sewer.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "chn": "……但我是不建议啦。",
      "jap": "…やめた方がいいと思うけどね",
      "eng": "Desperate measures, to be sure...",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "chn": "#0第3次完成交易后，互动列表-选择「交谈」",
      "jap": "#0リストから選択:話すC",
      "eng": "#0Menu-Choose \"Talk\" 3rd time after purchasing something",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "chn": "嗯……",
      "jap": "ふーむ…",
      "eng": "Hmm...",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "chn": "算了，你也算是个好顾客……",
      "jap": "まあ、君はいい取引相手だからね…",
      "eng": "You are a fine trading partner.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "chn": "不知道传说是否属实，\r\n但我听说残存的古龙居住在这个地方的某处。",
      "jap": "真偽も分からない噂だけど\r\nこの地のどこかに、古い竜の生き残りがいるらしい",
      "eng": "Rumour it may be, but I have heard of\r\na surviving ancient dragon who resides in this land.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "chn": "我还听说有几个不死人在服侍古龙，\r\n并为了成为龙而在修行。",
      "jap": "僅かな不死が古竜に仕え\r\n自らも竜になるために修行しているとも聞くよ",
      "eng": "A coterie of Undead serves the dragon,\r\nas they train to become dragons themselves.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "chn": "如果是真的，还真想见一面看看啊……",
      "jap": "もし本当なら、是非会ってみたいものだねえ…",
      "eng": "Sounds unlikely, but you never know, do you?",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "chn": "#0未完成交易，互动列表-选择「离去」",
      "jap": "#0リストから選択:立ち去る(何もしなかった)",
      "eng": "#0Menu-Choose \"Leave\" without purchasing something",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "chn": "这次真是遗憾啊。",
      "jap": "今回は、残念だったね",
      "eng": "Well, that is a shame, then.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "chn": "没关系，这种事没什么，别放心上。",
      "jap": "まあ、こんなこともあるさ。うん、うん",
      "eng": "But no matter. No, not to worry.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "chn": "下次看到我，记得和我打个招呼吧，我会等你的。",
      "jap": "懲りずに声をかけてくれよ、待ってるから",
      "eng": "Come back again. I'm always available.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
