      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": true
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "chn": "多谢。真棒的交易。",
      "jap": "ありがとう。いい取引だった",
      "eng": "Thank you. That was a fine trade.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "chn": "很期待下次再遇到你，",
      "jap": "君とは、また会えたら嬉しいな",
      "eng": "I have this funny feeling we'll meet again soon.",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "chn": "有缘再来笔好交易吧。",
      "jap": "素晴らしい取引をしようよ",
      "eng": "And we'll make another fine trade, of course!",
      "isUnused": false,
      "isTitle": false
